Acceptance Checklist
Windows should not be called polished until all of this is true:
Fresh install opens onboarding and pairs with Android and macOS without docs.
Trust prompt shows actual device ID/fingerprint/PIN and works.
Sending text, image, file, and multi-file works both directions.
Large file send does not allocate the full file in UI memory.
Active transfer controls work.
Activity feed persists across app restart.
Pending clipboard item can be applied, copied, resent, pinned, and deleted.
Settings save through the engine and survive restart.
Diagnostics can fix or explain common network/firewall/daemon issues.
All primary actions produce visible feedback.
Tray, hotkeys, jump list, Explorer context menu, notifications, and protocol handler are coherent.
App respects dark mode, high contrast, DPI scaling, keyboard navigation, and screen readers.
Windows CI builds the app and installer.
