Recommended Next Step
Start with Phase 0. The first concrete implementation should be the engine contract cleanup, visible feedback restoration, and pairing/trust repair. Visual redesign should come immediately after the app is honest about what works, because polishing a broken state contract will create a beautiful but unreliable shell.